DU (multiple Dwelling Units) solution including CEM-738 and CEM-7038 as the master bridges. They support up to 700/350 Mbps PHY/Throughput Rate as Distribution Backbone over Coaxial and up to 253 endpoints with isolation. For the endpoints, there are four endpoints to select depending on the demands. They are CES-730 for high speed data, CES-740 for high speed data plus voice, CES-760 for high speed data with MIMO 2X2 11n Wi-Fi and CES-750 for high speed data plus voice and MIMO 2X2 11n Wi-Fi.</p><p>CEM-7038 is the master bridge for the outdoors and it meets IP67 waterproof outdoor design. For the details of the products, please contact SendTek by e-mail at <a href="mailto:sales@sendtek.com" target="_blank">sales@sendtek.com</a> or by phone at 886-567-8666.</p>													</div>					</li><!--newsaccordion--></div><p><img src="images/line.png" ></p><div id="item2"> <ul> <li>2013 – HomePlug AV over Coax based EoC MDU Solution Announced</li><li>2012 – HomePNA3.1 based EoC MDU WiFi Endpoint Announced </li><li>2011 – HomePNA3.1 based EoC MDU Outdoor Master Announced</li><li>2010 – HomePNA3.1 based EoC MDU Voice Endpoint Announced</li><li>2009 – HomePNA3.1 Coax Home Networking Ethernet Bridge Announced</li><li>2008 – HomePNA3.1 Phoneline Home Networking Ethernet Bridge Announced</li><li>June, 2008 - CommunicAsia 2008 Show in Singapore.</li><li>October, 2007 - TelcoTV 2007 Show in Atlanta, USA.</li>  <li>March, 2007 - IPTV World Forum 2007 in London, England.</li><li>November, 2006 - TelcoTV 2006 Show in Dallas, USA.</li><li>June, 2006 - Globalcomm 2006 Show in Chicago, USA.</li><li>April, 2006 - HPNA/HCNA ADSL2+ Router Announced.</li><li>March, 2006 - 128Mbps HCNA Coax Management Bridge Announced.</li><li>March, 2006 - 128Mbps HPNA Management Bridge Announced.</li><li>March, 2006 - CeBIT 2006 Show in Hannover, Germany.</li><li>January, 2006 - 128Mbps HCNA Coax MDU Master Bridge Announced.</li><li>January, 2006 - CES 2006 Show in Las Vegas, USA.<